    <h1>Third-Party Cookies</h1>
    <p class="description">Data files set in your browser by a domain you did not visit directly. The backbone of cross-site ad tracking and retargeting — now <strong>blocked by default in Safari and Firefox</strong>, and in a state of flux in Chrome following Google's reversed deprecation plans.</p>
